SPM Opportunity Offshore Fund, Ltd.  Financing
SPM Opportunity Offshore Fund, Ltd. just submitted form D announcing  Indefinite financing.  SPM Opportunity Offshore Fund, Ltd. was able to sell $48,443,295. The total private offering amount was Indefinite. The financing was made by 29 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $5,000,000. The financing document was filed on 2014-09-23. SPM Opportunity Offshore Fund, Ltd. is based in  87 MARY STREET GEORGE TOWN GRAND CAYMAN KY1-9002. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  Christopher Russell.





